The paper focuses on gaze estimation using face and eye images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The proposed framework also involves attention mechanisms and machine learning models, which are relevant to multimedia (cs.MM), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
